un fir shvester zenen zey geven.

00:10:56.787 --> 00:10:58.232
ale umgekumen.

00:10:59.571 --> 00:11:01.573
hobn zey ale gevoynt in Gritse?

00:11:01.258 --> 00:11:02.048
NO

00:11:02.048 --> 00:11:03.193
AMSZCZONOW

00:11:03.773 --> 00:11:04.931
PRUSZKOW

00:11:06.760 --> 00:11:09.184
iz AMSZCZONOW geven vayt fun Gritse?

00:11:08.768 --> 00:11:09.397
NO

00:11:09.397 --> 00:11:11.647
UNK an etlekhe un tsvontsik kilometer.

00:11:11.805 --> 00:11:13.672
flegt ir tsunoyfkumen?

00:11:13.442 --> 00:11:17.638
ye. oyf yedere shul VACATION bin ikh geforn tsu mayn zeydn.

00:11:18.285 --> 00:11:19.781
dos heyst zumer.

00:11:19.483 --> 00:11:20.742
zumer, ye.

00:11:20.462 --> 00:11:21.890
az, ober

00:11:20.884 --> 00:11:23.310
shul VACATION, hob ikh gehat VACATION fun shul.

00:11:22.673 --> 00:11:26.329
ober durkhn yor akhuts zumer tsayt zent ir nisht tsunoyfgekumen?

00:11:25.930 --> 00:11:27.662
NO. ikh bin gegan in shul arayn.

00:11:28.545 --> 00:11:31.424
vos mit, bay di yontoyvim tsum bayshpil?

00:11:30.992 --> 00:11:36.082
yontoyvim zenen zey gekumen tsu undz, UNK di feters, di mumes gekumen tsu undz a sakh mol.

00:11:36.645 --> 00:11:39.221
hot ir gekent di bobes mit di zeydes?

00:11:38.721 --> 00:11:39.575
OH YEAH.

00:11:39.514 --> 00:11:41.027
vi hobn zey geheysn?

00:11:41.809 --> 00:11:45.532
mayn, eyn zeyde, di mame's foter, hot geheysn Shmuel

00:11:46.129 --> 00:11:48.097
un di bobe hot geheysn

00:11:48.559 --> 00:11:49.565
Perl

00:11:50.263 --> 00:11:52.012
un dem tatn's

00:11:52.120 --> 00:11:53.295
hot geheysn

00:11:53.318 --> 00:11:56.569
Khil der zeyde, un zi hot geheysn

00:12:01.113 --> 00:12:02.923
fargesn.

00:12:03.038 --> 00:12:06.457
velkhe kroyvim hot ir gehat in Gritse

00:12:07.172 --> 00:12:08.263
gufe?

00:12:07.206 --> 00:12:10.254
Gritse hob ikh gehat mayn tatn's a bruder, a feter

00:12:10.412 --> 00:12:11.452
Lozer

00:12:12.201 --> 00:12:13.258
umgekumen.

00:12:16.470 --> 00:12:18.894
vifl sinagoges zaynen geven in Gritse?

00:12:20.537 --> 00:12:24.733
eyn sinagoge un eyn besmedresh iz geven. ⟨a SYNAGOGUE⟩ zeyer a ⟨sheyn⟩.

00:12:25.093 --> 00:12:26.487
vi hot es geheysn?

00:12:29.008 --> 00:12:32.225
s'iz geven finef hundert yor hot ekzistirt di shul.

00:12:33.717 --> 00:12:36.073
bin gekumen nemen brider fun di shul.

00:12:39.133 --> 00:12:41.759
nisht vayt fun undz iz ⟨dort⟩ geven di shul

00:12:42.643 --> 00:12:44.982
un der daytsh hot es gevolt farbrenen.

00:12:46.896 --> 00:12:48.836
zenen gekumen di polyakn

00:12:48.836 --> 00:12:54.376
UNK dortn epes gevelblekh ⟨derlebn⟩, zey veln nisht untertsindn oyf a, m'vet zey ⟨shodn⟩

00:12:55.468 --> 00:13:02.178
hot er gezogt "OKAY, tserayst es, " hobn di polyakn UNK nemen UNK tserisn biz UNK a zeyger.

00:13:03.501 --> 00:13:05.081
ikh bin geshtanen derbay.

00:13:05.728 --> 00:13:07.038
ir hot dos gezen.

00:13:11.685 --> 00:13:15.459
vosere gesheftn, yidishe gesheftn, zaynen geven in Gritse?

00:13:17.153 --> 00:13:18.497
fun alerley

00:13:19.026 --> 00:13:22.597
SPOZYWCZY zakhn, fun manufaktur zakhn

00:13:22.671 --> 00:13:25.196
s'iz geven eyner a yid, zeyer a raykher

00:13:26.147 --> 00:13:27.659
hot gevoynt oyfn RYNEK

00:13:28.408 --> 00:13:30.832
farforn di daytshn azoy vi zey zenen arayn

00:13:30.973 --> 00:13:32.266
mit TRUCKn

00:13:32.475 --> 00:13:34.814
un eyner iz aroyf oyf a leyter

00:13:35.108 --> 00:13:35.754
un hot

00:13:35.754 --> 00:13:38.707
aroyfgevorfn oyf di TRUCKn di g- fule

00:13:38.707 --> 00:13:40.572
manufaktur vos iz g- ful

00:13:40.572 --> 00:13:46.746
⟨un⟩ di kleyne reshtelekh oyf di ⟨breterlekh⟩ hot er aroysgevorfn far di polyakn. di polyakn zenen geshtanen, zikh gefreyt un gekhapt.

00:13:50.025 --> 00:13:52.938
UNK iz dortn geven a sakh religyeze yidn?

00:13:53.080 --> 00:13:55.560
s'iz geven religyeze yidn oykh, YEAH, SURE.

00:13:55.273 --> 00:13:57.072
vos iz geven di batsiung

00:13:57.079 --> 00:14:00.414
tsvishn di religyeze un di nisht religyeze?

00:14:03.019 --> 00:14:05.747
UNK a batsiung. m'hot gornisht

00:14:05.753 --> 00:14:08.075
eyner dem andern nisht ge⟨UNK⟩ gornisht.

00:14:10.680 --> 00:14:13.174
ir hot gehert tsum, ah, dem bund, yo?

00:14:12.800 --> 00:14:13.350
ye.

00:14:13.174 --> 00:14:14.347
vos iz der bund?

00:14:14.347 --> 00:14:15.736
vos far a partey?

00:14:15.152 --> 00:14:17.373
dos iz a tsienistishe organizatsye.

00:14:18.038 --> 00:14:21.035
vegn vos flegt ir redn az ir zayt tsunoyfgekumen?

00:14:21.008 --> 00:14:25.187
m'hot gegat UNK krayzn. m'hot gelernt yidish shraybn un leyenen

00:14:25.648 --> 00:14:30.198
un azoy vayter. m'hot ge- farvaylungen. s'iz geven a biblyotek. s- geleyent bikher.

00:14:30.188 --> 00:14:32.004
iz geven tsienistish?

00:14:31.960 --> 00:14:32.814
NO.

00:14:33.208 --> 00:14:33.922
NO.

00:14:33.922 --> 00:14:36.561
NO, s'iz geven tsienistn ⟨in⟩ bazundere organizatsyes.

00:14:37.444 --> 00:14:39.733
zayt ir aleyn geven a tsienist?

00:14:39.587 --> 00:14:42.045
NO, ikh bin nisht geven keyn tsienist. geven a bundistke.

00:14:42.186 --> 00:14:47.040
hot ir a mol getrakht fun Yis- fun Palestine, Yisroel, tsu forn dortn?

00:14:46.540 --> 00:14:48.508
m'hot getrakht, ober

00:14:48.227 --> 00:14:49.858
s'iz nisht geven azoy vikhtik.

00:14:51.737 --> 00:14:54.785
vos mit tsaytungen? zaynen dortn geven tsaytungen?

00:14:54.285 --> 00:14:54.802
yo.

00:14:54.950 --> 00:14:56.894
s'iz geven a folks tsaytung.

00:14:55.028 --> 00:14:56.119
velkhe?

00:14:56.985 --> 00:14:59.088
s'iz geven a moment, s'iz geven a haynt.

00:14:59.724 --> 00:15:00.995
UNK tsaytungen.

00:15:01.120 --> 00:15:02.936
flegt ir leyenen di tsaytungen?

00:15:02.807 --> 00:15:06.007
ye, der folks tsaytung. mayn foter hot geleyent dem folks tsaytung.

00:15:08.292 --> 00:15:09.956
gedenkt ir als meydl

00:15:10.047 --> 00:15:12.521
velkhe khaloymes hot ir gehat?

00:15:13.860 --> 00:15:15.511
vos hot ir gevolt zayn?

00:15:15.511 --> 00:15:18.208
vos hot ir gevolt ton ven ir hot oysgevaksn?

00:15:20.222 --> 00:15:22.275
 ikh veys UNK zogn

00:15:29.014 --> 00:15:33.137
hot ir, ven ir, ir hot gekent ayer man fun kindvayz, yo?

00:15:33.027 --> 00:15:33.797
yo.

00:15:33.137 --> 00:15:35.235
zent ir geven zeyer noent?

00:15:35.376 --> 00:15:38.224
yo. m'iz gekumen ⟨in eyn⟩ organizatsye, UNK

00:15:38.224 --> 00:15:40.229
gegan mit zey far tsen yor.

00:15:40.911 --> 00:15:43.807
ven hot ir gevust az ir vet mit im khasene hobn?

00:15:44.404 --> 00:15:45.883
ven m'iz avekgeforn.

00:15:46.311 --> 00:15:47.604
ven iz dos geven?

00:15:49.129 --> 00:15:51.182
m'iz geven tsvey monat barn DEUTSCH.

00:15:51.205 --> 00:15:52.245
⟨geven⟩ tsvey monat.

00:15:52.960 --> 00:15:55.125
d- ir meynt in nayn un draysik?

00:15:55.125 --> 00:15:57.965
in nayn un, YEAH, in nayn un drays- in fer-

00:15:55.125 --> 00:15:59.033
nayn un draysik. in fertsikstn zenen mir avekgeforn, fertsikstn.

00:15:58.849 --> 00:16:04.445
ober ven ir zent aroys mit im durkh di ale yorn farn krig, hot ir gevust az ir vet mit im khasene hobn?

00:16:04.840 --> 00:16:06.285
hot ir gevolt?

00:16:05.228 --> 00:16:11.921
m'hot nisht geklert ⟨az me zol⟩ zakhn. s'iz nisht gekumen in kop arayn azolkhe zakhn. m'hot geklert der daytsh, der daytsh, UNK di gantse mishpokhe, m'iz avek.

00:16:11.877 --> 00:16:14.925
ikh meyn ober f- a sakh yorn far di daytshn

00:16:15.184 --> 00:16:16.595
ven ir hot im gekent.

00:16:20.500 --> 00:16:24.054
OKAY. vos nokh gedenkt ir fun der heym? vos nokh kent ir mir dertseyln

00:16:24.297 --> 00:16:25.438
fun Gritse

00:16:25.917 --> 00:16:28.661
ven ir zent geven a meydl farn krig?

00:16:32.278 --> 00:16:34.482
s'iz geven groyse antisemitizm.

00:16:34.590 --> 00:16:36.271
dos ken ikh dir zogn.

00:16:36.362 --> 00:16:38.178
m'hot a sakh gelitn.

00:16:39.028 --> 00:16:44.219
un mayne eltern hobn shver gearbet, BUT s- UNK skhoyre vos iz zeyer shver

00:16:44.395 --> 00:16:46.990
tsu heybn di ale zakhn, zeyer shver.

00:16:46.990 --> 00:16:49.012
mir hobn mir ale tsugeholfn.

00:16:49.339 --> 00:16:50.446
shvestern.

00:16:51.702 --> 00:16:55.612
mayn mame hot oykhet epes a s- barn daytsh, az s'iz gekumen di daytshn arayn, s'iz

00:16:55.612 --> 00:16:59.132
hobn zey aroysge⟨UNK⟩ di gantse skhoyre. zey hobn avekgefirt di skhoyre.

00:17:00.072 --> 00:17:02.344
biz shoyn leydike UNK

00:17:02.721 --> 00:17:07.676
s'iz nokh UNK kumen nokh ⟨iber⟩nemen. zogt di mame "ikh ze, s'iz dokh shoyn alts genumen. kh'hob dokh shoyn"

00:17:07.851 --> 00:17:11.743
hobn zey genumen, UNK di mame gehakt dem kop.

00:17:16.051 --> 00:17:19.555
az ir flegt dortn arbetn, aroyshelfn, vos hot ir geton?

00:17:21.385 --> 00:17:27.369
m'iz gekumen koynim, farpakt di teler, farpakt di glezer, farpakt di koyshn., s'iz shver arbet geven.

00:17:27.578 --> 00:17:30.575
ober m'hot geholfn, di mame zol nisht azoy fil arbetn.

00:17:32.995 --> 00:17:36.870
mayn muter hot dokh nokh nisht khasene gemakht keyn kind, zenen zey gekumen.

00:17:37.787 --> 00:17:40.329
mayn muter iz alt geven akht un fertsik yor.

00:17:42.968 --> 00:17:47.133
m'hot UNK zenen geven in Varshever geto. m'hot undz oysgetribn fun Gritse.

00:17:47.133 --> 00:17:47.672
nokh

00:17:47.672 --> 00:17:49.829
araynkumen UNK makht ⟨men shoyn⟩ a geto

00:17:50.494 --> 00:17:53.103
hobn zikh gevoynt UNK fuftsik mentshn in a shtub

00:17:54.595 --> 00:17:56.445
mayn tate iz gegan a bisl

00:17:56.445 --> 00:17:59.015
genumen a mentsh, m'hot im batsolt vifl er hot gegat

00:17:59.015 --> 00:18:02.185
me zol undz aroysnemen fun geto, ober UNK nisht gekent aroysgeyn fun geto

00:18:02.745 --> 00:18:06.890
iz er avek keyn Shidlovtse, a kleyn shtetele. dort iz geven UNK ⟨gezogt⟩ beser

00:18:07.943 --> 00:18:12.409
shoyn dort hot men zey arayngetribn ale yidn in a shul. UNK in di shul.

00:18:19.182 --> 00:18:21.724
dos iz geven tog fun rosheshone.

00:18:22.708 --> 00:18:23.950
in velkhn yor?

00:18:23.873 --> 00:18:25.402
dray un fertsikstn.

00:18:32.293 --> 00:18:37.299
ir gedenkt der tog, dem tog ven di milkhome hot zikh oysgebrokhn?

00:18:38.048 --> 00:18:39.560
ikh bin geshtanen in gevelb

00:18:39.718 --> 00:18:42.024
t- flien eroplanen. m'hot bombardirt

00:18:42.807 --> 00:18:47.053
di ershte bombe iz arayn in a mil arayn. s'iz geven UNK ⟨bay undz⟩ a mil in di gas arop.

00:18:47.717 --> 00:18:50.411
iz arayn di bombe, bald derharget eynem

00:18:50.805 --> 00:18:54.607
a yid. ikh gedenk UNK, a treger iz er geven, an oremer mentsh

00:18:54.607 --> 00:18:55.760
⟨SCHULTZ⟩

00:18:56.003 --> 00:19:02.021
er iz bald UNK a helft iz er geven farshotn, a helft in UNK, hot er geshrign "ratevet," UNK m'hot nisht gekent aroysnemen im.

00:19:02.753 --> 00:19:08.164
⟨BUT⟩ di DEUTSCHEN zenen gefloygn mit eroplanen. UNK niderik un geshosn keseyder vemen zey hobn gezen.

00:19:08.963 --> 00:19:12.028
hot men moyre gehat tsu geyn biz, UNK iz er nokh geblibn.

00:19:12.608 --> 00:19:15.116
hot ir farshtanen az s'iz a milkhome? hot ir

00:19:14.734 --> 00:19:15.453
vos far a frage.

00:19:16.135 --> 00:19:18.711
hot ir gevust foroys az zey kumen arayn?

00:19:19.307 --> 00:19:22.817
m'hot nisht forgeshtelt az s'vet aza milkhome zayn

00:19:22.817 --> 00:19:26.097
az m'vet nemen lebedike mentshn un brenen.

00:19:26.378 --> 00:19:27.792
ver hot zikh forgeshtelt?

00:19:27.792 --> 00:19:30.304
m'hot genumen kinder, m'hot tserisn oyf shtiklekh.

00:19:30.917 --> 00:19:32.193
ir hot dos gezen?

00:19:32.352 --> 00:19:34.590
kh'hob nisht gezen, nor ikh hob es geg-

00:19:35.845 --> 00:19:36.952
kh'hob es gehert.

00:19:37.633 --> 00:19:40.192
zenen ⟨gevezn⟩ a bakonter UNK in MONTREAL

00:19:40.350 --> 00:19:42.240
iz er meshuge gevorn mit dem.

00:19:42.240 --> 00:19:45.030
m'hot im aroysgerisn dos kind fun hant. m'hot es tserisn

00:19:46.020 --> 00:19:48.140
iz er meshuge gevorn, iz er geshtorbn.

00:19:49.648 --> 00:19:51.400
vos hot ir aleyn gezen

00:19:51.400 --> 00:19:53.894
mit di eygene oygn vos di daytshn hobn geton?

00:19:54.897 --> 00:19:56.629
ganen tsvey yidn

00:19:57.411 --> 00:19:59.312
zeyer ⟨bakovede⟩ yidn

00:20:00.027 --> 00:20:01.221
un

00:20:01.221 --> 00:20:04.526
zenen gan fun davenen tsi tsum davenen, nisht vikhtik

00:20:05.359 --> 00:20:08.036
hot men, zey hobn ⟨shtot gan⟩ in gas.

00:20:09.190 --> 00:20:10.950
⟨hobn⟩ DEUTCHEN tsu

00:20:10.950 --> 00:20:15.820
zenen geforn mit a MOTORCYCLE, zey hobn beyde yidn aroyfgevorfn oyf di MOTORCYCLE in keyshl.

00:20:15.820 --> 00:20:20.068
zey hobn zey aropgefirt nisht vayt fun unter di shtot, un hot men zey beyde dershosn.

00:20:23.618 --> 00:20:25.378
mir zenen bald antlofn.

00:20:25.378 --> 00:20:27.122
m'iz aroys in a dorf arayn

00:20:27.128 --> 00:20:28.269
in a VILLAGE

00:20:28.883 --> 00:20:31.656
zenen mir dort geven epes a tog tsi tsvey

00:20:31.656 --> 00:20:32.950
ikh gedenk shoyn nisht.

00:20:33.490 --> 00:20:35.964
m'iz tsurikgekumen, zenen shoyn DEUTSCHEN geven.

00:20:39.683 --> 00:20:43.558
m'hot eyn mol aroyfgekumen tsu undz bay di nakht, hot men dem tatn aroysgenumen fun bet

00:20:44.965 --> 00:20:50.831
iz UNK fun tate geven vays un di hor vays ⟨vi⟩ shney.

00:20:51.681 --> 00:20:53.649
iz er aroyfgan oyfn boydem

00:20:54.229 --> 00:20:57.193
zen ver s'iz dort do, iz keyner nisht geven oyfn boydem

00:20:57.891 --> 00:20:59.893
ober zey hobn nisht derharget demolt.

00:21:02.380 --> 00:21:04.568
UNK shreklekhe tsores.

00:21:05.890 --> 00:21:07.996
nu shoyn, mir ze'mir ⟨nakher⟩ avek.

00:21:07.996 --> 00:21:09.579
m'hot zey ale ibergelozt.

00:21:11.914 --> 00:21:14.928
mayne tsvey shvester zenen geblibn lebn in lager

00:21:15.390 --> 00:21:17.156
ober mayne krank-

00:21:19.407 --> 00:21:22.407
git tsu mir, git mir tsu farshteyn nokh a mol

00:21:22.407 --> 00:21:25.391
az di daytshn zenen a gla- arayn in Gritse

00:21:25.257 --> 00:21:26.967
dray tog hot genumen.

00:21:25.465 --> 00:21:26.184
in

00:21:26.747 --> 00:21:28.833
in nayn un draysik, in September

00:21:28.890 --> 00:21:29.592
yo

00:21:29.953 --> 00:21:33.322
un ir zent geven in a, geven in a dorf, hot ir gezogt?

00:21:32.980 --> 00:21:35.590
mir zenen antlofn, az zey hobn bombardirt gants

00:21:35.590 --> 00:21:37.070
k- di gantse shtot.

00:21:35.640 --> 00:21:38.303
az i- az ir zayt antlofn in a dorf?

00:21:37.986 --> 00:21:39.280
in a dorf arayn.

00:21:38.303 --> 00:21:39.819
in velkhn dorf?

00:21:41.142 --> 00:21:43.346
vi azoy hot es geheysn, dos dorf?

00:21:46.626 --> 00:21:48.932
ver iz antlofn? ir un ver nokh?

00:21:48.432 --> 00:21:51.244
mit mayn, mit mayn man's mishpokhe. ⟨er⟩ iz avekgeganen.

00:21:51.705 --> 00:21:55.394
un vos mit ayere dray shvester un mit, mit di eltern?

00:21:54.557 --> 00:21:57.538
zey zenen geven epes vu andersh gelofn, ikh veys. mir zenen gelofn

00:21:57.612 --> 00:22:01.453
di gantse shtot zikh tselofn di yidn, di yidn. polyakn zenen nisht antlofn.

00:22:01.645 --> 00:22:05.790
m'hot nisht gekhapt keyn polyak vayl er iz a polyak. a yid hot men gekhapt vayl er iz a yid.

00:22:07.517 --> 00:22:09.100
az ir zent antlofn

00:22:09.100 --> 00:22:11.696
un dernokh zent ir tsurikgekumen in Gritse?

00:22:10.500 --> 00:22:13.856
bin tsurikgekumen, iz dos gantse geven ofn, alts aroysgeroymt.

00:22:14.807 --> 00:22:17.990
un ir hot demolts gefunen di eltern un di shvester?

00:22:18.013 --> 00:22:19.863
yo, zenen ale aheymgekumen.

00:22:20.140 --> 00:22:23.323
ir hot no- zey hobn nokh gehat di, dos hoyz?

00:22:22.132 --> 00:22:24.182
yo, ikh hob dokh, iz yo, yo.

00:22:25.708 --> 00:22:28.351
vos nokh hot ir gezen ven ir zent tsurikgekumen?

00:22:30.687 --> 00:22:32.554
zaynen dortn geshtanen daytshn?

00:22:32.408 --> 00:22:35.625
yo, SURE. di gantse shtot iz geven ful mit daytshn.

00:22:36.070 --> 00:22:38.561
zent ir geven fray arumtsugeyn?

00:22:38.584 --> 00:22:41.008
m'hot moyre gehat aroystsu⟨geyn⟩ UNK.

00:22:43.640 --> 00:22:45.723
m'iz aribergelofn ⟨dem⟩ RYNEK fun shtub tsu

00:22:45.729 --> 00:22:46.762
UNK

00:22:46.762 --> 00:22:48.112
m'hot moyre keseyder.

00:22:49.097 --> 00:22:50.424
hot ir ge-

00:22:49.418 --> 00:22:52.736
ober in anfang iz geven ruik, iz nakher gevorn ruik.

00:22:52.776 --> 00:22:59.132
m'hot oyfgemakht dos gevelb. m'hot UNK bisl skhoyre UNK gehat hot men nokh gehandlt vi s'iz. hot men nokh ayn⟨UNK⟩ azoy di yidn.

00:22:59.897 --> 00:23:03.657
ober nakher hot ⟨es⟩ shoyn gemakht fun undz, zenen mir nisht geven. ikh bin avek in

00:23:03.657 --> 00:23:05.260
keyn Rusland UNK

00:23:05.260 --> 00:23:08.970
nokh derhaltn a briv funem tatn fun Varshe in lager

00:23:10.022 --> 00:23:13.796
hot er geshribn "tayere kinder, antloyfts, ⟨ver vu ets⟩ kent."

00:23:16.384 --> 00:23:17.745
shoyn UNK gornisht ⟨gehert⟩.

00:23:18.460 --> 00:23:20.650
az demolst ven ir zent tsurik

00:23:20.650 --> 00:23:21.823
keyn Gritse

00:23:21.823 --> 00:23:25.763
iz der tate un di mame nokh, zen- zenen, zenen nokh alts geven

00:23:22.973 --> 00:23:26.745
ale UNK gelebt, yo, yo.

00:23:25.763 --> 00:23:26.773
in shtetl.

00:23:26.982 --> 00:23:29.220
un vi lang iz es geven azoy

00:23:29.226 --> 00:23:31.515
vos ir zayt ⟨es⟩ geven tsuzamen in Gritse?

00:23:31.858 --> 00:23:33.371
ven m'iz geven tsuzamen?

00:23:32.871 --> 00:23:33.759
yo.

00:23:34.052 --> 00:23:36.476
unter di, zeks vokhn.

00:23:34.103 --> 00:23:35.450
bay zeks vokh.

00:23:36.938 --> 00:23:39.398
un in di zeks vo- vokhn

00:23:39.398 --> 00:23:41.825
hot ir ongefirt vayter di gesheft?

00:23:41.713 --> 00:23:48.254
zeyer v- zeyer UNK. eyn mol iz der tate geforn keyn Varshe, iz men geforn keyn Varshe nokh skhoyre aynkoyfn

00:23:48.328 --> 00:23:51.236
iz geven bar undzere TRUCKS, groyse TRUCKS

00:23:51.236 --> 00:23:53.790
zey hobn undz gefirt di skhoyre fun Varshe

00:23:54.775 --> 00:23:56.726
ir hot gekent, NO, ir hot nisht gekent Varshe.

00:23:57.340 --> 00:24:00.669
UNK ayngekoyft di skhoyre, farpakt oyf UNK oyf

00:24:00.669 --> 00:24:03.932
TRUCKS un geforn oyfn veg. hobn DEUTSCHEN opgeshtelt dem TRUCK

00:24:04.056 --> 00:24:09.079
m'hot aropgenumen dem DRIVER, a yid s'iz geven, a yungen mentsh.

00:24:10.637 --> 00:24:12.419
zey hobn im dershosn

00:24:13.135 --> 00:24:17.499
nakher hobn zey im farbrent. zey hobn aheymgeshikt a kestele ash tsu di froy.

00:24:18.670 --> 00:24:21.971
mayn foter UNK keyn Varshe

00:24:23.344 --> 00:24:25.228
eyner UNK avek UNK

00:24:31.343 --> 00:24:34.627
hot im azoy lang geshlogn, hot er nisht gekent UNK lebn

00:24:35.393 --> 00:24:38.208
un di mame iz arumgeforn vi azoy vi a UNK

00:24:38.208 --> 00:24:43.217
me zol UNK avek. UNK ober er iz shoyn nisht geven keyn mentsh.

00:24:43.948 --> 00:24:46.929
un shoyn, dos iz geven ⟨nokh dem⟩ farbrent.

00:24:51.424 --> 00:24:53.527
dos iz geven der tate, ir zogt?

00:24:52.900 --> 00:24:54.550
der tate, mayn tate.

00:24:54.310 --> 00:24:55.839
un ven iz dos geven?

00:24:57.634 --> 00:25:01.121
⟨eyder⟩ UNK geforn fun Gritse, ⟨dem⟩ fertsikstn yor.

00:25:02.713 --> 00:25:05.424
az dos iz geven nokh ⟨di⟩ etlekhe vokhn

00:25:05.785 --> 00:25:08.496
vos ir zent tsurikgekumen fun, fun derfl.

00:25:14.509 --> 00:25:18.485
hot ir gekent etlekhe penemer fun di polyakn

00:25:19.065 --> 00:25:20.345
etlekhe vos?

00:25:19.065 --> 00:25:23.885
ho- hobn polyakn aroy- i- vos hobn aroysgeholfn di daytshn

00:25:24.111 --> 00:25:25.151
hot ir

00:25:24.128 --> 00:25:27.432
ikh hob nisht gekent azelekhe, ah, vos hobn UNK geholfn daytshe?

00:25:27.432 --> 00:25:29.572
nayntsik protsent hobn geholfn di daytshn.

00:25:29.545 --> 00:25:31.952
ho- hot ir gekent etlekhe penemer

00:25:32.059 --> 00:25:35.259
fun gevezene shkheynim oder gevezene

00:25:35.485 --> 00:25:36.525
koynim?

00:25:37.223 --> 00:25:40.490
m'hot gegat mit zikh tsu tun. m'hot nisht gekukt gornisht.

00:25:41.188 --> 00:25:44.354
m'hot nor moyre gehat, antlofn far di bintl

00:25:44.547 --> 00:25:48.962
lebn UNK azoy vi mayz, zenen mir dokh geven ⟨hungerik⟩ azoy vi mayz.

00:25:52.545 --> 00:25:56.052
az vos iz gevorn in fertsik? der tate hot im geshlogn

00:25:56.052 --> 00:25:57.619
un nokh dernokh?

00:25:57.118 --> 00:25:59.710
in UNK iz er geven in Varshe.

00:25:59.633 --> 00:26:03.019
m'hot im genumen in Varshe. un di mame oykh?

00:26:01.354 --> 00:26:02.704
dem

00:26:02.704 --> 00:26:07.584
NO, dem tatn, un dem, un dem DRIVER hot men bald dershosn, un zey hobn farbrent

00:26:07.584 --> 00:26:10.034
dos ash hobn zey geshikt tsu di froy ⟨keyn⟩ UNK

00:26:10.180 --> 00:26:11.473
a yunger mentsh.

00:26:12.103 --> 00:26:15.067
un vos iz gevorn mit di shvester un mit der mamen?

00:26:15.647 --> 00:26:19.618
UNK m'hot dokh aroysgetribn fun Gritse ale, ale yidn.

00:26:19.618 --> 00:26:22.594
m'hot aroysgetribn fun Gritse ale yidn.

00:26:22.853 --> 00:26:25.277
m'hot zey araynge⟨kumen⟩ keyn Varshe in a geto

00:26:25.772 --> 00:26:29.849
hot in eyn shtub gevoynt eyn ROOMele a kleyns UNK tsvontsik mentshn.

00:26:30.683 --> 00:26:33.512
ir, m'hot aykh gefirt in a, oyf a ban?

00:26:34.294 --> 00:26:36.763
yo. KONSKI vagonen, KONSKI

00:26:36.763 --> 00:26:38.186
ferd vagonen.

00:26:39.205 --> 00:26:40.847
vi lang hot dos genumen

00:26:40.847 --> 00:26:42.776
tsu forn biz Varshe?

00:26:42.327 --> 00:26:44.633
nu, a por sh- a shtunde ⟨oykh⟩ nisht.

00:26:46.866 --> 00:26:50.617
s'iz UNK di mame genumen, hot gehat a bisl zakhn.

00:26:50.617 --> 00:26:54.847
hot avekgegebn dort epes eynem. zey hobn mir gezogt di shvester UNK nisht geven

00:26:54.847 --> 00:26:57.557
ven m'hot aroysge⟨UNK⟩ fun Gritse bin ikh shoyn nisht geven, bin antlofn

00:26:58.020 --> 00:27:01.136
az ⟨zey hobn⟩ mir getsolt epes gelt ⟨hot er gegebn⟩ zakhn

00:27:01.142 --> 00:27:03.262
me zol aroysnemen zikh fun geto

00:27:03.775 --> 00:27:05.794
hot er undz aroysgenumen fun geto

00:27:06.542 --> 00:27:08.257
hot aroysgenumen fun geto

00:27:15.503 --> 00:27:18.619
zenen zey geforn keyn Shidlovtse, a kleyn shtetele

00:27:19.030 --> 00:27:22.989
mayn foter hot gehat dort epes a feter tsi a zeyde tsi a bobe, veys nisht.

00:27:23.164 --> 00:27:26.178
dort zogt er iz shtil, efsher vet men nor blaybn lebn

00:27:26.691 --> 00:27:33.958
un dort di ershte por tog zenen zey geshlofn, hot men gedungen epes in a STORE, a nare hot men zikh gemakht, UNK gelign oyf di nare.

00:27:38.250 --> 00:27:41.568
es iz geven a goy vos hot gearbet ⟨oyf⟩ di UNDERGROUND

00:27:42.672 --> 00:27:47.593
UNK geven a bakonter goy. mayn shvester iz shoyn geven in dem lager, in SKARZYSKO

00:27:49.101 --> 00:27:51.474
hot er gebrengt ale mol fun di mamen

00:27:52.493 --> 00:27:56.182
a fatsheyle, ikh zol tsudekn, nokh UNK. ⟨dos iz mayn muter⟩.

00:27:56.644 --> 00:28:01.464
un zi hot aroysgeshikt a shtikl broyt, UNK avekgenumen fun moyl, ikh zol hobn a shtikl broyt

00:28:01.875 --> 00:28:05.585
iz UNK gekumen tsurik UNK a shtikl broyt, ⟨ikh zol⟩ vayter

00:28:05.585 --> 00:28:06.785
zogt zi di

00:28:06.785 --> 00:28:08.906
m'hot shoyn farbrent ⟨dayn⟩ mame mitn tatn.

00:28:09.165 --> 00:28:10.745
s'iz geven UNK

00:28:14.633 --> 00:28:16.466
shreklekhe ⟨zakh⟩

00:28:18.784 --> 00:28:21.478
in di geshikhte iz nokh nisht dos geven

00:28:22.058 --> 00:28:25.140
me ken zikh nisht forshteln vos zey hobn ⟨tsu⟩ undz ongetun.

00:28:30.175 --> 00:28:35.248
yo, ⟨biz⟩ UNK geven in Rusland. mayn mame UNK geveynt, ⟨gemeynt⟩ ikh lebn shoyn nisht.

00:28:38.832 --> 00:28:40.547
oy vey.

00:28:52.686 --> 00:28:57.641
az ir hot mir dertseylt epes frier, vegn, az di daytshn zenen aroyf in boydem

00:28:58.170 --> 00:28:59.969
dos iz geven in Gritse?

00:28:59.332 --> 00:29:00.792
in Gritse in di heym.

00:29:00.792 --> 00:29:04.307
in shtub UNK bay di nakht.

00:29:04.684 --> 00:29:06.990
dos iz eyder m'hot aykh aroysgetribn.

00:29:07.010 --> 00:29:09.436
yo, eyder m'hot aroys⟨UNK⟩ keyn Varshe, yo.

00:29:07.097 --> 00:29:08.241
hobn zey gezukht

00:29:09.713 --> 00:29:13.591
⟨ikh zog dir⟩ shreklekhe zakhn, UNK shoyn nisht geven, nokh alemen geven.
